strings: <voice_0x01001622><se_def>*: I've been waiting for you meddlesome fools! Your pitiful attempts to stop me have been in vain!

<voice_0x01001623><se_def>*: Behold, I am the Lord of Darkness, Rhapthorne! My resurrection to flesh has
been a long and painful journey.

<voice_0x01001624><se_def>Rhapthorne: And what pitiful circumstances we have all
had to endure along the way! But, humans!
Now I will unite us in happiness!
<voice_0x01001625><se_def>Rhapthorne: From this moment, the World of Light and the World of Darkness will be as one! And this union shall herald the reign of a new ruler!

<voice_0x01001626><se_def>Rhapthorne: One almighty power to preside over all!
The Lord of Darkness, Rhapthorne!

<voice_0x01001627><se_def>Rhapthorne: You will revere me!
And you will offer up your pitiful lives as
a mark of your respect and adoration!
